description:
&lt;p&gt;We currently have vacancy within our busy emergency department for a Reception supervisor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This key role will lead our reception staff to provide a high quality, comprehensive and professional administration service in support of the clinical activities undertaken in the Emergency Department. Knowledge of NHS emergency administration, excellent communication, customer service, and core IT skills are essential, however training will be provided for specific NHS IT administration&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The current vacancy is full time 37.5 hours (1.0wte)* Predominant working days M-F however some work-shift work covering 24/7 is required inc. nights&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you wish to discuss this further please contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Senior sister Andrea.Hill@ouh.nhs.uk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 11-Nov-2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Andrea.Hill@ouh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
